text: Ines Gmati (born 5 April 1997) is a Tunisian sailor. At the 2016 Summer Olympics she competed in the Women's laser radial. ==References== Category:Tunisian female sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Tunisia Category:1997 births Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser Radial Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:African Games gold medalists for Tunisia Category:African Games medalists in sailing Category:Competitors at the 2011 All-Africa Games
